00:18:34.630 --> 00:18:37.447
environment will hold for
the next year, two years?

00:18:37.447 --> 00:18:40.030
Or do you think we're going to
eventually sees some increases?

00:18:40.030 --> 00:18:41.110
GINO BLEFARI: I think we're
going to eventually see

00:18:41.110 --> 00:18:41.890
some increases.

00:18:41.890 --> 00:18:44.022
I have no idea how long it will.

00:18:44.022 --> 00:18:45.730
Everybody was forecasting
it would go up,

00:18:45.730 --> 00:18:47.640
and then something in
the economy will happen

00:18:47.640 --> 00:18:48.800
and it will go down.

00:18:48.800 --> 00:18:51.630
I think what you need to
understand about interest

00:18:51.630 --> 00:18:54.220
rates, when the Fed
raises interest rates,

00:18:54.220 --> 00:19:00.770
