sources of information

00:19:16.920 --> 00:19:21.880
that we could find that wouldn't
require us to have MLS access?

00:19:21.880 --> 00:19:24.870
GINO BLEFARI: Well, real
estate's local, number one.

00:19:24.870 --> 00:19:27.180
So every market's different.

00:19:27.180 --> 00:19:30.040
And of course, I come from
the real estate industry.

00:19:30.040 --> 00:19:32.320
So I would say
you've got to find

00:19:32.320 --> 00:19:35.670
somebody that understands
that market and knows

00:19:35.670 --> 00:19:36.510
what's going on.

00:19:36.510 --> 00:19:41.190
There was a time a
while-- not so much now--

00:19:41.190 --> 00:19:44.500
