00:20:21.830 --> 00:20:24.420
all sorts of things
right there on the--

00:20:24.420 --> 00:20:27.010
And Berkshire Hathaway isn't
the only one with that app,

00:20:27.010 --> 00:20:29.280
but there's all
sorts of ways to.

00:20:29.280 --> 00:20:30.790
That's a way to
almost get access

00:20:30.790 --> 00:20:33.650
to all of the MLS yourself.

00:20:33.650 --> 00:20:35.480
JORDAN THIBODEAU: Right.

00:20:35.480 --> 00:20:38.030
In case of a
deflationary environment,

00:20:38.030 --> 00:20:40.400
how can we position
real estate assets?

