00:21:34.480 --> 00:21:35.930
and casualty insurance.

00:21:35.930 --> 00:21:38.410
Can you explain how all
those entities work together?

00:21:38.410 --> 00:21:41.610
GINO BLEFARI: Yeah,
most big companies

00:21:41.610 --> 00:21:45.220
like Berkshire Hathaway
Home Services, Home Services

00:21:45.220 --> 00:21:49.150
of America is the second
largest real estate

00:21:49.150 --> 00:21:51.180
company in the country.

